Create a modern AI education platform for Turkish students with the following features:

DESIGN REQUIREMENTS:
- Dark theme with purple/blue gradient backgrounds
- Modern, clean student-friendly interface
- Card-based layout with rounded corners and shadows
- Smooth hover animations and transitions
- Professional educational platform look

CORE FEATURES:
1. Authentication System:
   - Login page with email/password
   - Register page for new students
   - Form validation and error handling

2. Dashboard Layout:
   - Left sidebar navigation with icons
   - Main content area
   - Responsive design for mobile/desktop

3. Navigation Pages:
   - Dashboard (homepage with overview)
   - Chat (AI conversation interface)
   - Documents (chat history and saved conversations)
   - Profile (student information and settings)

4. Chat System:
   - Real-time chat interface with AI
   - Subject selection dropdown (Matematik, Fen Bilgisi, Türkçe, İngilizce, Tarih)
   - Message bubbles for user and AI responses
   - Typing indicator
   - Message history display

5. Additional Features:
   - Student profile management
   - Dark/light theme toggle
   - Responsive mobile design
   - Clean typography with good readability

TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS:
- React with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Lucide React for icons only
- Modern ES6+ JavaScript
- Clean, production-ready code
- No external UI libraries (pure Tailwind)

STYLING GUIDELINES:
- Primary colors: Purple (#8B5CF6) and Blue (#3B82F6) gradients
- Dark background (#0F172A, #1E293B)
- White text on dark backgrounds
- Cards with subtle shadows and hover effects
- Modern button styles with gradients
- Clean spacing and typography

Make this a complete, working application that a Turkish student can use for educational AI assistance. All text should be in Turkish where appropriate.